Front end

As a full-stack web developer, I am proficient in a variety of front-end technologies and frameworks.

These include:

HTML CSS JavaScript React Bootstrap Using these tools, I am able to create engaging, responsive, and user-friendly web applications.

Back end

In addition to front-end development, I am also proficient in a variety of back-end technologies and frameworks. These include: Node.js: a JavaScript runtime used for server-side programming Express.js: a Node.js web application framework used for building APIs and web servers MongoDB: a NoSQL database used for storing and retrieving data Mongoose: an object modeling tool used with Node.js and MongoDB to simplify database operations RESTful APIs: a web service architecture used for creating scalable and maintainable APIs JSON: a data interchange format used for transmitting data between the client and server Using these tools, I am able to build robust and scalable web applications that can handle large amounts of data and traffic.
